An output packet can hold up to 8 TPs.

vdm_out_pkt_t: PKO SG pointers for a output packet (1 cmd + 8 TP segments)

outpkt_t:  output packet, holding vdm_out_pkt_t and jib_commands

sgchunk_list_t: chunk of outpkt_t (contains pointer to array of outpkt_t)

core_outpkt_t: array of sgchunk_list (64 lists)


